      "date": "2011-09-07 01:53:24.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on rhel/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/cf45d28e-d8f1-11e0-8d02-52540025f9af).  Ran 12 tests.  No failures.",
